title: Printer's Sample Book, 1883–84
creditline: Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts
description: Small leather notebook with handwritten formulas for dyestuffs for printed textiles. Contains 160 samples of printed fabric.

tombstone.epitaph:
Printer's Sample Book, 1883–84.
1883–84. Medium: leather, cardboard, cotton. Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts. 1945-55-22.
